title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from a table containing a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row should not throw an exception.
SR:
To reproduce the bug: 
1. Add a table to the report that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 
2. Preview the report. 
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
